ng>\r\n<em>Solid Void</em>, Progetto Diogene, Turin, Italy, November, 7–13, 2011. Workshop curated by Roberto Cuoghi and Gian Antonio Gilli.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2013</strong>\r\n<em>Arimortis</em>, Museo del Novecento, Milan, Italy, April 5 – September 8, 2013, group exhibition curated by Roberto Cuoghi and Milovan Farronato, in collaboration with DOCVA Documentation Center for Visual Arts.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2015</strong>\r\n<em>Ametria</em>, Benaki Museum, Pireos St., Athens, Greece, June 12 – October 11, 2015, curated by Nicoletta De Rosa, Polina Kosmadaki, Alessandro Pasini, Tomaso Piantini, and Yorgos Tzirtzilakis. Group exhibition based on an idea by Roberto Cuoghi, organized by the DESTE Foundation for Contemporary Art in collaboration with the Benaki Museum.', 'Exhi & Bio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '744-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-10-30 17:25:10', '2018-10-30 16:25:10', '', '744', 'https://www.robertocuoghi.com/744-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
