005, Gagosian Gallery, Berlin, curated by Anna-Catharina Gebbers. Presented in the context of the 4th Berlin Biennale, the exhibition brought together private collections of various artists, including some preserved sea animals from Cuoghi’s collection.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>2002</strong>\r\nDaily News, New York’s Hometown Newspaper, project curated by Aleksandra Mir, New York, USA, September 11, 2002.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<strong>1999</strong>\r\n<em>In Camera Caritatis</em>, Globale Positionen 10, Museum in Progress, Vienna, Austria, curated by Massimiliano Gioni. (Conceived for this project, the work was presented on a double page of the newspaper Der Standard, Vienna, December 27, 1999).', 'Exhi & Bio', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '744-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-11-18 23:20:00', '2018-11-18 22:20:00', '', '744', 'https://www.robertocuoghi.com/744-revision-v1/', '0', 'revision', '', '0'),
